Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.12,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(500,122)}为海盗所擒\N\N接受拷问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命——！
